## Dataset Availability

The datasets used in this study are publicly available through Google Drive.

📂 **Download Dataset:** [Click here to access the dataset](https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1ZNNrLlSb7GIvuvNFKMNDHEvGxci6WppK?usp=sharing)

The shared folder contains the processed datasets used for CWEMAP evaluation, including the TreeVul and PrimeVul train, validation, and test splits.

### Download from Terminal

You can also download the dataset using `gdown`:

```bash
pip install gdown

gdown --folder "https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1ZNNrLlSb7GIvuvNFKMNDHEvGxci6WppK?usp=sharing" -O ./datasets
